01:11:20.790 --> 01:11:22.980
and he's been attacked quite a bit.

01:11:22.980 --> 01:11:24.483
He's a controversial figure.

01:11:25.440 --> 01:11:27.780
What's the role of the
university to protect

01:11:27.780 --> 01:11:29.190
the Jordan Petersons of the world?

01:11:29.190 --> 01:11:33.090
- I think the university
has an absolute, absolute,

01:11:33.090 --> 01:11:35.380
not relative, that absolute

01:11:36.450 --> 01:11:39.450
obligation to protect the academic freedom

01:11:39.450 --> 01:11:43.233
of even the most
controversial faculty members.

01:11:44.220 --> 01:11:48.210
And you can imagine,
on a university campus,

01:11:48.210 --> 01:11:50.970
you have more people who are outliers

01:11:50.970 --> 01:11:53.373
than you do in the general population.

01:11:56.340 --> 01:11:57.840
- [Lex] That's the hope, at least.

01:11:57.840 --> 01:11:58.833
- Hopefully. Yeah.

01:12:01.093 --> 01:12:03.273
And those outliers have to be protected.

01:12:04.530 --> 01:12:06.540
They can't be pressured,
they can't be fired,

01:12:06.540 --> 01:12:11.540
they can't be disabled
from spewing their views,

01:12:11.580 --> 01:12:13.050
whether they're considered racist,

01:12:13.050 --> 01:12:17.419
whether they're considered
to promote an idea

01:12:17.419 --> 01:12:21.273
of human society that's
considered obnoxious.

01:12:22.860 --> 01:12:23.880
It doesn't matter.

01:12:23.880 --> 01:12:27.950
If you can't have freedom of thought

01:12:27.950 --> 01:12:31.620
on the college campuses, where can you?

01:12:31.620 --> 01:12:34.140
Then we're lost. As a society, we're lost.

01:12:34.140 --> 01:12:37.530
And as an educational institution,

01:12:37.530 --> 01:12:40.110
educational institutions
no longer will educate.

01:12:40.110 --> 01:12:42.120
They will indoctrinate.

01:12:42.120 --> 01:12:44.160
That, we have to avoid at all costs.

01:12:44.160 --> 01:12:46.650
- And we should also
remember that the outlier

01:12:46.650 --> 01:12:49.920
might also be the only bearer of truth.

01:12:49.920 --> 01:12:54.900
So, in Nazi Germany, speaking
against the fascist regime.

01:12:54.900 --> 01:12:58.500
In communist Soviet Union,
speaking against communism.

01:12:58.500 --> 01:13:02.490
They might hold the key to the solving

01:13:02.490 --> 01:13:03.660
the ailments of that society.

01:13:03.660 --> 01:13:04.980
- Absolutely.

01:13:04.980 --> 01:13:07.680
And some of the most important
discoveries in science,

01:13:07.680 --> 01:13:08.513
for example,

01:13:10.706 --> 01:13:13.800
were mocked at the beginning.

01:13:13.800 --> 01:13:16.627
I mean, think of poor Charlie Darwin.

01:13:16.627 --> 01:13:18.360
- "Charlie". (chuckles)

01:13:18.360 --> 01:13:21.780
I see he is on nickname levels with you.

01:13:21.780 --> 01:13:24.300
Well, 'cause we're talking
about these big topics

01:13:24.300 --> 01:13:26.360
