01:13:26.360 --> 01:13:28.410
We should not forget
about the smaller topics,

01:13:28.410 --> 01:13:30.360
which might even have
the much bigger impact,

01:13:30.360 --> 01:13:33.280
which is what you're speaking to, which is

01:13:34.770 --> 01:13:35.980
outlier

01:13:37.110 --> 01:13:38.490
ideas in science.

01:13:38.490 --> 01:13:43.110
So, basically welcoming
controversial ideas in science.

01:13:43.110 --> 01:13:45.420
And by "controversial", I mean just stuff

01:13:45.420 --> 01:13:48.840
that most of the community
doesn't agree on.

01:13:48.840 --> 01:13:50.850
It doesn't actually harm anyone at all.

01:13:50.850 --> 01:13:53.100
