empowered by the administration,

01:14:05.520 --> 01:14:10.320
where young faculty that
come in, they're kind of, um-

01:14:10.320 --> 01:14:11.820
- [Harvey] Pre-tenured.

01:14:11.820 --> 01:14:16.110
- Yeah, there's a
process in chasing tenure

01:14:16.110 --> 01:14:18.690
where you're kind of supposed to behave,

01:14:18.690 --> 01:14:21.900
and there's an incentive
to kind of fit in,

01:14:21.900 --> 01:14:23.760
and to not be an outcast,

01:14:23.760 --> 01:14:27.360
and that's a really huge
problem because, oftentimes,

01:14:27.360 --> 01:14:31.440
the youth is when the
craziest, the biggest ideas,

01:14:31.440 --> 01:14:34.950
the revolutionary ideas come
and if you're forced to behave

01:14:34.950 --> 01:14:37.500
and fit in and not speak out,

01:14:37.500 --> 01:14:39.810
then even in the realm of science,

01:14:39.810 --> 01:14:41.370
the innovation is stifled.

01:14:41.370 --> 01:14:46.200
- Well, now you trigger my,
