01:17:50.520 --> 01:17:51.813
Now, listen to this.

01:17:53.070 --> 01:17:55.620
This was a freshman orientation.

01:17:55.620 --> 01:17:56.943
The administrators,

01:17:58.560 --> 01:17:59.997
the deans and the deanettes,

01:17:59.997 --> 01:18:02.547
