deans and deanettes,

01:18:02.547 --> 01:18:06.660
and the third-deputy
assistant deans and deanettes,

01:18:06.660 --> 01:18:10.530
lined the students up,
according to their skin hues.

01:18:10.530 --> 01:18:11.460
- [Lex] Oh, boy.

01:18:11.460 --> 01:18:16.230
- The blonde, blue-eyed
white folks were at one end.

01:18:16.230 --> 01:18:17.440
The darkest

01:18:21.450 --> 01:18:25.740
African Americans whose
bloodlines had not yet

01:18:25.740 --> 01:18:28.623
mixed with any of the
whites, on the other end.

01:18:29.970 --> 01:18:34.620
And the exercise was, you
had to tell how your race

01:18:34.620 --> 01:18:38.763
affected your success in
life, up until that point.

01:18:41.370 --> 01:18:44.850
I thought it was the most demeaning thing

01:18:44.850 --> 01:18:47.340
that one could imagine.

01:18:47.340 --> 01:18:48.660
Demeaning.

01:18:48.660 --> 01:18:50.167
I thought to myself,

01:18:50.167 --> 01:18:53.070
