about sexual orientation.

01:18:53.070 --> 01:18:55.050
They could do the same about religion.

01:18:55.050 --> 01:18:57.060
They could do the same
about national origin.

01:18:57.060 --> 01:19:00.120
It would be demeaning, no matter what."

01:19:00.120 --> 01:19:01.753
- [Lex] Yeah.

01:19:01.753 --> 01:19:03.310
- And the students actually

01:19:04.680 --> 01:19:08.250
verbalized how their race

01:19:08.250 --> 01:19:10.530
had either been a plus or a minus.

01:19:10.530 --> 01:19:12.600
- They did it?
- They did.

01:19:12.600 --> 01:19:14.340
And I thought it was so demeaning.

01:19:14.340 --> 01:19:19.340
It just confirmed all of my
distaste for this kind of,

01:19:20.670 --> 01:19:22.320
this kind of approach.

01:19:22.320 --> 01:19:24.180
- Let me ask you from
