or dictators,

01:20:03.960 --> 01:20:05.850
people who are seen as evil?

01:20:05.850 --> 01:20:09.660
- Well, we want face
the world with reality.

01:20:09.660 --> 01:20:13.366
And the reality is that
there is some unpleasantness,

01:20:13.366 --> 01:20:16.140
unpleasantnesses in the world.

01:20:16.140 --> 01:20:18.120
Running from genocide,

01:20:18.120 --> 01:20:23.120
right through to ordinary
discrimination, to offensiveness.

01:20:23.670 --> 01:20:26.850
It's the real world, as we know it exists.

01:20:26.850 --> 01:20:28.413
Are we afraid to say it?

01:20:29.370 --> 01:20:31.980
Do we wanna make people
think that we live in a world

01:20:31.980 --> 01:20:34.080
where those words are not used?

01:20:34.080 --> 01:20:36.603
Where those animosities don't exist?

01:20:38.040 --> 01:20:39.240
The answer is no.

01:20:39.240 --> 01:20:40.380
- But you can whitewash,

01:20:40.380 --> 01:20:42.030
you can normalize the use of those words,

01:20:42.030 --> 01:20:45.870
