01:20:50.831 --> 01:20:54.090
1937, '38, those are all
different dynamics there,

01:20:54.090 --> 01:20:58.080
but you can normalize this
person, and in so doing,

01:20:58.080 --> 01:21:00.450
create enormous harm.

01:21:00.450 --> 01:21:02.460
- Well, see, I don't
see it as normalizing.

01:21:02.460 --> 01:21:04.680
I see it as exposing.

